✅ Variables
- Used to store data.
- No need to declare type

name = "Praveen"
age = 30
pi = 3.14


✅ Constants
• 	Python doesn’t enforce constants, but use UPPERCASE by convention.

MAX_RETRIES = 5

✅ Comments
- Single-line: # This is a comment
- Multi-line:
"""
This is a multi-line comment.
Useful for documentation.
"""
